[src:atlantic-ocean/atlantic-ocean-p02] 44% of stocks are being fished at unsustainable levels.
[src:atlantic-ocean/atlantic-ocean-p02] In the southeast Atlantic catches have decreased from 3.3 million tons in the early 1970s to 1.3 million tons in 2013.
